{"_id":"qKjKIsOwrp30XGZi","name":"Cheval","permission":{"default":0,"fQMz3jO6Mtr33nDi":3},"type":"creature","data":{"characteristics":{"str":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.STR","label":"CHARAC.Strengh","formula":"(3D6+18)*5"},"con":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.CON","label":"CHARAC.Constitution","formula":"(2D6+6)*5"},"siz":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.SIZ","label":"CHARAC.Size","formula":"(6D6+12)*5"},"dex":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.DEX","label":"CHARAC.Dexterity","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"app":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.APP","label":"CHARAC.Appearance","formula":""},"int":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.INT","label":"CHARAC.Intelligence","formula":""},"pow":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.POW","label":"CHARAC.Power","formula":"(3D6)*5"},"edu":{"value":null,"short":"CHARAC.EDU","label":"CHARAC.Education","formula":""}},"attribs":{"hp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Hit points","auto":true},"mp":{"value":null,"max":null,"short":"HP","label":"Magic points","auto":true},"lck":{"value":null,"short":"LCK","label":"Luck"},"san":{"value":null,"max":99,"short":"SAN","label":"Sanity","auto":true},"mov":{"value":"12","short":"MOV","label":"Movement rate","auto":false},"db":{"value":null,"short":"DB","label":"Damage bonus","auto":true},"build":{"value":null,"short":"BLD","label":"Build","auto":true},"armor":{"value":null,"auto":false}},"status":{"criticalWounds":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"unconscious":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"dying":{"type":"Boolean","value":false},"tempoInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"indefInsane":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"personalDescription":{"type":"string","value":""},"special":{"attribs":{"move":{"primary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null},"secondary":{"enabled":false,"value":null,"type":null}}},"sanLoss":{"checkPassed":null,"checkFailled":null},"attacksPerRound":1},"infos":{"type":""},"flags":{"locked":true,"initialized":true,"displayFormula":false},"biography":{"personalDescription":{"value":"<p>Les chevaux offrent de nombreux avantages &agrave; qui sait les apprivoiser. Dans le cadre du jeu, on distingue les chevaux de monte, les chevaux de trait et les &acirc;nes et mules.</p>\n<p>La comp&eacute;tence &eacute;quitation concerne les chevaux de monte. Un petit groupe de cavaliers peut facilement couvrir une soixantaine de kilom&egrave;tres en une journ&eacute;e, s&rsquo;il dispose d&rsquo;eau et de foin ou d&rsquo;autres nourritures en abondance. Les chevaux de monte peuvent se chamailler entre eux, mais ils ne se battent pas &agrave; moins d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre encercl&eacute;s. M&ecirc;me la formation des montures utilis&eacute;es dans la cavalerie se limite &agrave; calmer leur nervosit&eacute; et &agrave; les habituer &agrave; la d&eacute;tonation des armes. Presque tous les chevaux paniquent en pr&eacute;sence de forces surnaturelles.</p>\n<p>Robustes et vigoureux, les chevaux de trait sont g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement d&eacute;bourr&eacute;s, quoiqu&rsquo;ils servent rarement de montures. Lorsqu&rsquo;ils tirent une cal&egrave;che ou une diligence, on les dirige &agrave; l&rsquo;aide de la comp&eacute;tence Conduite d&rsquo;attelage. Il n&rsquo;existe pas n&eacute;cessairement de selles et de harnachements &agrave; leur taille. Monter &agrave; cru impose un d&eacute; malus en &eacute;quitation. Les &acirc;nes et les mules sont des animaux de b&acirc;t plut&ocirc;t que de monte. Ils peuvent aussi tirer des charrettes ou des chariots. L&rsquo;expression &laquo; t&ecirc;tu comme un &acirc;ne &raquo; vient de leur tendance &agrave; ignorer les ordres qui leur d&eacute;plaisent, m&ecirc;me sous les coups.</p>\n<p>Tous les chevaux auront la m&ecirc;me r&eacute;action sens&eacute;e face &agrave; la violence, les coups de feu, les monstres ou les foules en col&egrave;re : la fuite.</p>\n<h3>Combat</h3>\n<p><strong>Attaques par round : </strong>1</p>\n<p><strong>Options de Combat rapproch&eacute; :</strong> La ruade n&rsquo;est pas la seule attaque de ces animaux. Outre leur morsure dangereuse, ils peuvent exploiter leur taille en bousculant des adversaires plus petits, ou se cabrer pour les &eacute;craser de leurs pattes avant. Un cheval doit &ecirc;tre entra&icirc;n&eacute; pour pi&eacute;tiner des fantassins.</p>\n<p><strong>Protection :</strong> aucune.</p>\n<p><strong>Habitat : </strong>prairies et d&eacute;serts, ou dans les zones civilis&eacute;es.</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Beasts/Horse.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Cheval","displayName":0,"img":"modules/CoC7-compendiums-fr/pictures/photos/CoC7%20Books/Beasts/Horse.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"actorId":"qKjKIsOwrp30XGZi","actorLink":false,"actorData":{},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"WxeKyFUUOlfpjETK","flags":{},"name":"Combat rapproché","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":0,"value":"25","attributes":{},"properties":{"combat":true,"fighting":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":100000},{"_id":"YN4zOZQq4Sk09XPF","flags":{},"name":"Sabots","type":"weapon","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"Creature's natural attack","chat":"Creature's natural attack","special":""},"wpnType":"innate","skill":{"main":{"name":"Combat rapproché","id":"WxeKyFUUOlfpjETK"},"alternativ":{"name":"","id":""}},"range":{"normal":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":"1D8"},"long":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""},"extreme":{"value":0,"units":"","damage":""}},"usesPerRound":{"normal":1,"max":null,"burst":null},"bullets":null,"malfunction":null,"blastRadius":null,"properties":{"addb":true,"slnt":false,"melee":true,"rngd":false},"eras":{},"price":{}},"sort":200000},{"_id":"pZDvf7PiVXe2I6bU","flags":{},"name":"Esquive","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","data":{"specialization":"Combat rapproché","description":{"value":"<p>Comp&eacute;tence primordiale, elle permet d&rsquo;&eacute;viter les coups, les armes de jet et d&rsquo;autres attaques dangereuses. Un investigateur peut esquiver autant de fois que n&eacute;cessaire dans le m&ecirc;me round de combat, mais une seule fois par attaque (cf. Chapitre 6 : Combat). Toutefois, il ne peut esquiver que les attaques qu&rsquo;il voit venir. Ainsi, il est impossible d&rsquo;esquiver les balles, puisqu&rsquo;on ne les voit plus bouger une fois en mouvement. Le mieux que l&rsquo;on peut faire est de prendre des mesures d&eacute;fensives, pour se rendre plus difficile &agrave; toucher (cf. Se mettre &agrave; couvert, page 100).</p>\n<p>L&rsquo;Esquive progresse avec l&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience, comme n&rsquo;importe quelle comp&eacute;tence.</p>\n<h2>Comp&eacute;tence oppos&eacute;e / Niveau de difficult&eacute; :</h2>\n<p>Servant essentiellement lors de tests oppos&eacute;s en combat, l&rsquo;esquive n&rsquo;a pas de difficult&eacute; fixe.</p>\n<p><strong> Note :</strong> En tant que comp&eacute;tence de combat, le redoublement est impossible.</p>","opposingDifficulty":"","pushedFaillureConsequences":"","chat":""},"base":"@DEX/2","value":"25","attributes":{},"properties":{"fighting":false,"firearm":false,"combat":true,"special":true},"eras":{},"flags":{}},"sort":300000}]}
